</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BBB36ECFFF0F61E8CB938EEF9E6F2F9" blockId="52.[1444,2652,3235,3475]" pageId="52" pageNumber="110">
Populations attributed to 
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFF0F61E8E3D38EEF806F288" authorityName="Bergmans &amp; Sarbini" authorityYear="1985" box="[1827,1955,3314,3347]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Dobsonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="110" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="emersa">D. emersa</taxonomicName>
