Schouten Is (Numfor, Biak-Supiori, and Owi) off NW New 
<collectingCountry id="F313767CFFF0F61E80813971F5A2F211" box="[2463,2567,3437,3466]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="52" pageNumber="110">Guinea</collectingCountry>
